# Gmail Configuration
# Get app password from: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
EMAIL_USER=your-email@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASS=your-16-char-app-password

# Notes:
# 1. You MUST use a Gmail App Password (16 characters), not your regular password
# 2. Enable 2-Factor Authentication first at https://myaccount.google.com/security
# 3. Then generate App Password at https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
# 4. Copy this file to .env and fill in your actual credentials
# 5. Never commit .env to version control
# 6. For GitHub Actions, add these as repository secrets
